file.name: openapi3.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0

info:
  title: Parrot Test Api
  description: test api
  contact: {}
  version: '1.0.0'

servers:
- url: http://{defaultHost}
  variables:
    defaultHost:
      default: www.example.com/parrot-test

paths:
  /robin/location:
    get:
      summary: RobinLocation_GET
      operationId: RobinlocationGet
      parameters: []
      responses:
        200:
          description: ''
          headers: {}
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
        500:
          description: failed to find robin
      deprecated: false

  /robin/catchphrases/{id}:
    get:
      summary: RobinCatchphrasesById_GET
      operationId: RobincatchphrasesbyidGet
      parameters:
      - name: id
        in: path
        description: ''
        required: true
        style: simple
        explode: false
        schema:
          type: integer
          format: int32
      responses:
        200:
          description: ''
          headers: {}
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
        500:
          description: failed to find catchphrase
      deprecated: false

  /batman/location:
    get:
      summary: BatmanLocation_GET
      operationId: BatmanlocationGet
      parameters: []
      responses:
        200:
          description: ''
          headers: {}
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
              example: batcave
        500:
          description: failed to find batman
      deprecated: false

tags: []

Error: notImplemented: path "/batman/location": get: responses: 200: contents: unsupported content types: [text/plain]
